						               													<description>Crime Story is a fast-paced story-telling game where players together build fascinating criminal stories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game players use cards depicting items, characters, places and actions. One after another, they build sentences to create the most consistent criminal story they can tell. A player who tells the sentence is called an AUTHOR. If  the AUTHOR speaks out loudly sentence containing a word present on a card in other player's hand, the AUTHOR takes that card and puts it face up in front of him. This card gives him 1 point at the end of the game. A player who has the most points at the end of the game is a winner so during the game you should try to lead the story in a way that will protect cards that you have at your hand. Also be careful! There is a murderer among you. He tries to outrun others by getting additional points. Can you tell the best story and meanwhile hunt down the murderer?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
